data.description: Discover effortless living in this single-level haven located in Billings’ west end!  Embrace the comfort and accessibility with 3 bedrooms, 2 bath, and no stairs – just comfort, perfect for effortless living.  Enjoy the upgraded quartz counters, vaulted ceilings, commercial grade LVP flooring, white kitchen, gas range, tile shower, wide doorways, AND a built-in generator. Sprawling owners suite, designed for ultimate relaxation.  The yard is fenced and has UGSP. Convenience meets luxury with an oversized attached 3 car garage with an extra tall garage door, ensuring ample space for all your needs and BONUS: it's ADA compliant.   Your perfect oasis awaits you.
